    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persons who perform the dramatic entertainment known as mime, where action and emotion are conveyed without words, using gestures and bodily movements.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
